在批评碧昂斯之后，莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）正在与乡村音乐和西方音乐一起“尝试一些东西” https://www.nme.com/news/music/after-criticising-beyonce-beyonce-lily-ally-ally-trying-country-country-music-music-3750196?utm_source = rss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = fter-campaign = ferter-campeightter-campeightter-critication-criticis-criticati乡村音乐Tom SkinnerWed, 24 Apr 2024 14:22:52 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3750196 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯（左）和莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）（右）的两张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艾伦说，这种类型对她的歌曲创作风格“很好”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/after-criticising-beyonce-lily-allen-trying-country-music-3750196">莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）在批评碧昂斯（Beyoncé）之后的帖子正在“尝试一些东西”，而西方音乐</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯（左）和莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）（右）的两张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/LilyAllen-Beyonce-country-music-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）</a>透露，在批评<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯（Beyoncé</a> ）最近进入该类型的过程之后，她正在与乡村音乐中“尝试一些东西”。</p><p>在她<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/brand/p0hhgmp6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>想念我吗？</em></a>播客，艾伦（Allen）以前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-shares-thoughts-on-beyonces-weird-cover-of-jolene-3613736">分享了她对碧昂斯（Beyoncé）版本的经典曲目“乔琳（Jolene）”的想法</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">。</a></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">碧昂丝 - “牛仔卡特”评论：乡村重新发明罢工黄金</a></strong></li></ul><p>艾伦解释说：“很奇怪，您会涵盖该类型中最成功的歌曲。” “当您想解决一种新类型时，我只是觉得这是一件有趣的事情，而您只需选择该类型中最大的歌曲即可。”</p><div class="sc-hpEguC TiCsR"><div class="sc-bkSUFG bdkDcZ"><p>她继续说：“我的意思是，你愿你，碧昂丝 - 她真的在做她，但是她为什么要做多莉？”</p><p>在尼克·格里姆肖（Nick Grimshaw）和安吉拉·哈特内特（Angela Hartnett）的<a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/19eW4YQ0UaAuHpGO2ufCRR?si=c9281d54df964987" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>菜肴</em></a>播客的最新一集中，艾伦（Allen）说，她目前正在研究新材料时探索乡村和西方音乐。</p><p>她（通过<a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/lily-allen-recording-new-country-music-criticising-beyonce-cowboy-carter-dish-podcast-b1153555.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>标准</em></a>）解释说：“我只是为一些音乐腾出一些空间，以示出一些音乐。”</p><div class="sc-hpEguC TiCsR"><div class="sc-bkSUFG bdkDcZ"><div><div><p> “这不是专辑……是的。我只是，您知道，尝试一些东西，看看它是否有效。我确实喜欢乡村音乐和西方音乐。而且我觉得自己的写作是讲故事的，有点像叙事主导的音乐。” </p><p><iframe title="Spotify嵌入：Lily Allen和Miquita Oliver，香肠和洋葱肉汁" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/19eW4YQ0UaAuHpGO2ufCRR?si=c9281d54df964987&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="article-bottom"><div class="sc-dJiZtA coVQkW"><div class="sc-kCMKrZ jFrYkm"><div class="sc-iLsKjm jwZpEa topic-tag"><div class="sc-hpEguC TiCsR"><div class="sc-bkSUFG bdkDcZ"><div><div><p>艾伦补充说：“因为我没有感觉，所以这绝不是关于情感的。所以……是的，乡村和西方音乐很好地借出了自己。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-has-been-in-nashville-working-on-new-music-its-quite-intimidating-being-here-3613836">艾伦（Allen）透露她一直在田纳西州纳什维尔（Nashville）开发新材料</a>后，这被称为世界音乐之都。</p><p>她说：“在纳什维尔有很多遗产。” “我不得不说，在这里非常令人生畏。人们真的很有才华。”</p><p>艾伦（Allen）的第四张和最新录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lily-allen-no-shame-review-2326933#:~:text=And%20'My%20One'%20is%20a,pretty%20unique%20point%20of%20view.">“ No Shame”（No Shame）</a>于2018年发行。</p><p>本月初， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/azealia-banks-hits-back-at-lily-allen-over-beyonce-cowboy-carter-criticism-youre-going-to-stop-right-there-and-sit-this-one-out-3614789">Azealia Banks对艾伦对碧昂丝的批评做出了回应 - 告诉歌手和演员“坐下来”</a> 。她还指责“微笑”艺术家过去的种族主义言论。 </p></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-boJDB iuuckD full-bleed-1000"><div class="sc-fUnMCh lmuWgJ"><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/azealia-banks-slams-beyonces-cowboy-carter-as-white-women-cosplay-3607552">Banks自己在“ Cowboy Carter”上击中</a>，说碧昂丝在“白人女角色扮演”中。她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/azealia-banks-tells-beyonce-youre-setting-yourself-up-to-be-ridiculed-again-over-new-country-album-3586845">早些时候声称，这位歌手通过冒险进入国家“使自己变得嘲笑”</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="NME遇到莉莉·艾伦" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/O0qhqTEylmU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a>将于今年晚些时候发行一张名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-announces-new-country-album-lasso-3580491">“ Lasso”</a>的乡村专辑。在其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/post-malone">马龙（Post Malone）</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-and-post-malone-will-reportedly-feature-on-beyonces-cowboy-carter-3610753">在“牛仔卡特（Cowboy Carter）”歌曲“ Levii&#39;s牛仔裤”上的特色</a>）嘲笑了自己进入该类型的举动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/now-the-ting-tings-have-gone-country-too-on-new-song-danced-on-the-wire-3611496">同时，最近在社交媒体上共享一些即将到来的国家风格材料的片段</a>。</p><p>碧昂丝（Beyoncé）最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-becomes-first-black-woman-to-land-us-number-one-country-album-with-cowboy-carter-3614606">成为第一位与“牛仔卡特（Cowboy Carter）”获得美国第一次乡村专辑的黑人女性</a>。 2月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-becomes-first-black-woman-to-hit-number-one-on-us-country-chart-3590558">她以单曲“ Texas Hold&#39;Em”的身份成为第一个进入美国国家榜首的黑人妇女</a>。</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/after-criticising-beyonce-lily-allen-trying-country-music-3750196">莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）在批评碧昂斯（Beyoncé）之后的帖子正在“尝试一些东西”，而西方音乐</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
